# Copy to `.env.production` before `npm run build` when the API is not on the same host as the static files.
# No trailing slash.
#
# On **Vercel** with `vercel.json` proxying `/apimobile` and `/api` to nodeteam.site: leave this unset so the
# browser calls `https://YOUR-APP.vercel.app/apimobile/...` (same origin) and the edge proxies to Node.
# Set VITE_API_ORIGIN only if you intentionally want the browser to call the API host directly (CORS must allow your app).
# VITE_API_ORIGIN=https://nodeteam.site
